[[File:Shri Mangeshi Temple, Goa.jpg|thumb|right|Shri Mangesh Devastan, Prioll.]]'''Shri Mangesh Devastan''' gõyantolem namnechem deusthan. Hem fonddem talukeantlea [[Prioll]] gamvant [[Ponnji]]-[[Moddgamv]] hea mukel rosteacher [[Ponnji]]saun sumar 21 ki.mi. ontracher asa. Hem devull jea vattharant asa, tea vattharak mongexi mhunn vollkhotat.

==Itihas==
Purvil'lea kallant hem devull [[Saxtti]] talukeachea [[Kuxstholli]] va [[Kutthtthalli]] hea vattharant axil'lem.

[[Porxuraman]] gomontokant vosoupakhatir Trihotr purasaun doxgotri brahmonn ani tanchi 64 kullam haddlim mhonnttat. Hea kullamni [[Mongexi]], [[Xantadurga]], [[Nagex]], [[Mohalkxmi]], [[Soptokottexrvor]], [[Mohalosa]] adi aplea kuldeutancheo protimai haddun [[Gõy]]ant sthapon keleo. Tatuntolem [[Mongex]] doivt mull [[Kuxstholli]] hangam sthapon kel'lem.

[[File:Shri Mangesh.jpg|thumb|right|Scan of a wallet card depicting Shri Mangesh]]Fuddem i.So.1510t Gõyacher Purtugezanchi sot'ta yetkoch tamnnim hanga [[Hindu]] dhormiancho chholl, battabatti, devaloyancho vidhvoms korpachem sotr choloilem. Jen'na [[Kuxstholli]]chea Xri Mongex deusthanachea kullavi lokank khubor koll'lli ki [[Purtugez]]amni saxtti talukeantlea lokank battoun thoinchea devaloyancho nax korpacho kottrochola, ten'na tamnni ratorat gupitonnan [[Mongex]] devachem ling ukhlun xezarchea adiloxohachea rajeant zom-i [[Hindu]] sordar tevellar odhikaracher axil'le, thoim fonddem talukeachea prioll gamvant vhorun sthapon kelem.

==Sthapna==
Hi sthapna xalivahon xoke 1482 roudr nam' somvtsori mhollear i.So. 1560 vorsa zali oxi mhaiti tea deusthanachea purvil'lea itihasant melltta.

Hem stholantor 1me 1560 hea disa adi zalem oxem kompaji-i de Jhezhuschea padri monddllan tea kallant boroun douril'lea ani aplea vorixtthank sador kel'lea ohvalant boroil'lem asa.

Stholantorak lagun hea devaloyachi imarot tea [[Jhezhuitt]] padrimni aple chorchikhatir vaproli ani aplea dhormacheo deuta thoim sthapon keleo osoi tatunt ul'lekh melltta.

==Prioll vattharant==
[[Kuxstholla]] saun [[Prioll]] vattharant stholantor kortokoch thoim bandil'lem devull koxem axil'lem hachovixim mhaiti mellna.

Uprantochem dusrem devaloi [[Moratthexahichea]] voibhou kallant bandil'lem. Tacheuporant i.So.1890 to teach zagear tisre khepek devull handlem.

Chouthe khepe hea deulacho jirnnodhdar xoke 1894 magh xukl punvent purai zalom ani teach disa sumhurtacher 17 Februvari 1973 disa Xri [[Mongex]] devachea devaloyacher bhangracho kolos bosoilo. Dor vorsa hea devaloyant magh xukl punve disa mohaprvonni utsou monoitat.

==Xibikotsou==
Hea devasthanant dor somara ratcho xibikotsou zata.

Hea devasthanache kulavi Vats ani Kandinea hea donuch asAat. Hea devasthanat agrasohalachi sai aasa.
